                    <value>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;Hi {{{Recipient.FirstName}}},&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
You&amp;#39;ve committed to optimizing your health, and we&amp;#39;re here to support you every step of the way.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif&quot;&gt;Please take a few moments to complete your monthly wellness check-in below.&lt;strong&gt; This helps us identify what&amp;#39;s working, where we can make improvements, and how to support you better on your path to optimal health.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif&quot;&gt;1. Have there been any changes to your prescription&amp;#39;s or supplements?&lt;br /&gt;
2. Have you noticed any changes in your body composition?&lt;br /&gt;
3. Are you experiencing any challenges staying on the program?&lt;br /&gt;
4. What kind of diet are you currently following? (Carnivore,Keto,Low Carb,Paleo, Intermittent Fasting, Plant-Based, etc)&lt;br /&gt;
5. How much water are you drinking daily?&lt;br /&gt;
6. What is your current daily protein intake (in grams)&lt;br /&gt;
7. How often are you exercising each week?&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Please rate the following areas of your health, with 1 being the lowest and 10 being the best:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Sleep Quality&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Diet Quality&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Energy Level&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Stress Level&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Libido&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Mental Clarity&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Recovery (muscle,stamina,fatigue)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Digestion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Final Question (I promise!)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;How can I support you better to help you reach your health goals this month?&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Please reply directly to this email. You&amp;#39;re doing incredible work-and we&amp;#39;re here to help you stay consistent,confident, and 10X better every day.&lt;/p&gt;

